    <item>
      <title>欧盟着眼于五月份批准乌克兰改革，以释放更多援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/eu-eyes-ukraine-reform-approval-in-may-in-bid-to-unlock-more-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正准备于 5 月份批准乌克兰的改革计划，该计划将额外发放 19 亿欧元（合 20 亿美元），作为欧盟今年计划向基辅提供的总计 159 亿欧元财政援助的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/eu-eyes-ukraine-reform-approval-in-may-in-bid-to-unlock-more-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 16:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰图斯克敦促欧盟利用冻结的俄罗斯资产帮助乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/poland-s-tusk-urges-eu-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克周四表示，欧盟应该利用俄罗斯冻结的资产来帮助乌克兰，因为仅使用意外利润是不够的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/poland-s-tusk-urges-eu-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员梅嫩德斯妻子的贿赂案审判将分开审理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/senator-menendez-wife-s-bribery-trial-will-be-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅南德斯 (Bob Menendez) 的贿赂案审判将按计划于 5 月继续进行，尽管他妻子的案件因医疗问题将被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/senator-menendez-wife-s-bribery-trial-will-be-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰武器库存耗尽，美国的挫败感加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-frustration-mounts-as-ukrainian-weapon-stocks-run-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，随着人们越来越担心俄罗斯军队可能在未来几周内取得重大进展，拜登政府对国会共和党人和欧洲盟友因拖延为乌克兰对抗俄罗斯的战斗提供资金而感到更加沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-frustration-mounts-as-ukrainian-weapon-stocks-run-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司人工智能投资的“互联网络”令英国 CMA 担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/google-apple-microsoft-get-ai-antitrust-scrutiny-from-uk-cma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc.旗下谷歌、苹果公司和微软公司对人工智能的投资值得英国反垄断监管机构进行更深入的审查，因为担心它们被利用来进一步巩固其市场力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/google-apple-microsoft-get-ai-antitrust-scrutiny-from-uk-cma</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰核电站袭击促使紧急监管机构召开会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ukraine-nuclear-plant-attacks-prompt-emergency-watchdog-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能监督机构在维也纳召开紧急会议，讨论俄罗斯占领的乌克兰一座核电站发生事故的风险日益增加的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ukraine-nuclear-plant-attacks-prompt-emergency-watchdog-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治分歧迫使法国放弃能源目标法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/france-drops-plan-to-put-energy-targets-into-law-amid-political-rift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于议会中反对核能和可再生能源的政治分歧，法国放弃了将中期能源目标写入法律的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/france-drops-plan-to-put-energy-targets-into-law-amid-political-rift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国国防部长在丘吉尔活动中将普京比作希特勒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/german-defense-chief-compares-putin-to-hitler-at-churchill-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托利斯将俄罗斯总统普京对乌克兰的战争与阿道夫·希特勒1938年吞并捷克斯洛伐克领土进行了比较，并表示欧洲应该为俄罗斯的大规模袭击做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/german-defense-chief-compares-putin-to-hitler-at-churchill-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国林德纳表示无需进一步承担欧洲债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/germany-s-lindner-says-no-need-for-further-european-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，在各国财务状况恢复正常之前，欧盟不应为进一步的项目提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/germany-s-lindner-says-no-need-for-further-european-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权公司因在交易审查中隐瞒信息而受到调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/justice-department-scrutinizing-private-equity-merger-disclosure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员周三表示，美国司法部正在调查一些私募股权公司是否在交易审查期间故意向反垄断执法者隐瞒信息，以避免收购被阻止的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/justice-department-scrutinizing-private-equity-merger-disclosure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
